name: Inman's Cave
description:
This is one of the only caves in Maine that requires the use of SRT equipment. The cave is small but makes for a fun adventure. Location beta and more information can be provided by contacting the Maine Cave Survey with the following email: stephen.whitney1999@gmail.com

If you have visited this cave please do not post location data to keep riffraff out of dangrous situations!
